data.description: Welcome to this spacious and inviting townhome located in the highly sought-after Neshaminy Valley Neighborhood. This home offers and abundance of living space and modern amenities, making it perfect for comfortable family living . The generously sized living room seamlessly blends into a dining area, providing ample space for hosting gatherings or enjoying family meals. A recently renovated kitchen with contemporary finishes opens up to a cozy family room, creating  a central hub for daily activities and quality  time with loved ones.  Upstairs, the second floor master bedroom complete  with full bath,  Two additional well-lit bedrooms share a hallway bathroom. This townhome offers a spacious modern interior for comfortable living and a location that provides easy access to schools and shopping  area. contact us today to schedule a viewing by showing time.
